@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName "WenQuanYi Zen Hei"
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor black
  FontColor black
}
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
  BorderColor black
}
top to bottom direction

rectangle "行迹应变·多人出行动态规划与中断恢复平台" as system #E8E8E8

rectangle "账号管理\n注册、登录、注销、忘记密码、个人资料管理" as account
rectangle "社交组队管理\n好友关系管理、出行小组管理、房间码加入" as social
rectangle "出行规划管理\n成员约束、初始方案、节点、地图、预算" as planning
rectangle "监测与应变管理\n事件、影响、风险、持续分析、重规划、投票、变更、通知" as adaptive
rectangle "社区管理\n讨论区、攻略社区、一键套用、行后游记" as community
rectangle "后台与监控管理\n用户管理、运营后台、统计分析、可观测与配置" as admin

system -down-> account
system -down-> social
system -down-> planning
system -down-> adaptive
system -down-> community
system -down-> admin

account -[hidden]right-> social
social -[hidden]right-> planning
planning -[hidden]right-> adaptive
adaptive -[hidden]right-> community
community -[hidden]right-> admin
@enduml
